               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I had been four years and eleven months serving in a man of war; I got paid off; I went about, and lost all my money; a man came and said, "I can put you in a way to get a few shillings, take this out, and this pass, and I will give you 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.;" I was taking it out, and was taken.</p>
